"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"The director of the United Nations' World Food Programme laid out a plan to spend **$6.6 billion** to combat world hunger â€” a direct response to a back-and-forth with Tesla CEO Elon Musk, who claimed he would sell Tesla stock to fund a plan if the WFP could describe \\\"exactly how\\\" it would work.\\n\\nIn the document Beasley posted, the WFP proposes dedicating $3.5 billion to buy and deliver food directly, $2 billion \\\"for cash and food vouchers (including transaction fees) in places where markets can function,\\\" and spending another ***$700 million*** to manage new food programs that are \\\"adapted to the in-country\\\" conditions and ensure \\\"the assistance reaches the most vulnerable.\\\"\\n\\nAnother $400 million would be used for \\\"operations management, administration and accountability\\\" and supply chain coordination.\",\"timestamp\":1637316475,\"title\":\"UN to Elon Musk: Here's that $6 billion plan to fight world hunger\"},\"digest\":\"23GuvyEgsVSANLhKdWsMK8YwnMZQi9JJ0sn8gdJ5Jhg\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xBC4563889cAFdA55279c56596837C8374dE16AB1\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"f18kR4WkQBsEVPeXB58JokgCgqazTfe3v1IXokA25Xk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"mE2yB4touT0E962rfMSzxLEOTsRoeSHA4LSA_LudPHE\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"DRNhQ7KyMrT2DsDNXSiAVTc97m7CwGvyODaGzi_JVyGaE3bpFPOD-ambb4IJhGM2d1cJpe_kS97-XTeR9eFPlA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x8426ebf29262327d01034b8f702adffba337d998c4295bbc51cb188cb575ea0b533a1373e0b8b38c0b144faf2c1c9ad93482f51ab0df42b3472c71032eea4e141b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"f18kR4WkQBsEVPeXB58JokgCgqazTfe3v1IXokA25Xk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"mE2yB4touT0E962rfMSzxLEOTsRoeSHA4LSA_LudPHE\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-